ygData.messageBody:
oasis is a good place to hunt at your level, I soloed there all the way
from 16 to 17. I was killing Crocidiles, no loot but good exp. if you group
there is a few orc camps you can hunt at for loot, they drop bronze weapons
and raw-hide armor
